								<td width="285" valign="top"><p><img src="images/century_plaza.jpg" width="275" height="185" /></p></td>
								<td><p><strong>Hyatt Regency Century Plaza Hotel </strong>(Congress Hotel)<br />
									<GEO TYPE="US">2025 Avenue of the Stars<br />
									Los Angeles, CA 90067</GEO><br />
									<a href="http://www.centuryplaza.hyatt.com" target="_blank">http://www.centuryplaza.hyatt.com</a></p>
									<p>Hotel Telephone Number:&nbsp;&nbsp;(310) 228-1234<br />
										Toll Free:&nbsp;&nbsp;(800) 233-1234</p>
									<p>The Hyatt Regency Century Plaza Hotel is located in the heart of Century City on Los Angeles&#8217; fashionable West Side, adjacent to Beverly Hills and Rodeo Drive.The property overlooks the ABC Entertainment Center and sits across the street from Westfield Shoppingtown.</p>
									<p>The hotel is minutes by freeway to sandy beaches, Universal Studios and Disneyland and 25 minutes to the airport.</p>
									<p>The Hyatt Regency Century Plaza Hotel offers the following special rates for WCCM Participants:</p>
									<p>Singles: $149.00<br />
										Double/Twins: $169.00<br />
										Additional person: $25.00</p>
									<p class="alert"><strong>Please note: This hotel currently has limited availability.</strong></p>
									<p>The hotel offers the following amenities for Congress participants:</p>
									<ul>
										<li>Free wireless internet access in meeting rooms and most public areas.</li>
										<li>Free high-speed internet access via cyber-stations in the exhibition hall.</li>
										<li>Reduced parking fee of $10 per day for self-parking and $15 per day for valet parking.</li>
									</ul>
									<p>For online room reservations, please visit the hotel website (http://www.centuryplaza.hyatt.com), select check-in and check-out dates, and specify Group/Corporate number <span class="alert"><strong>G-UCLA</strong></span>.&nbsp;&nbsp;You may also contact the hotel directly for room reservation using the telephone numbers above.&nbsp;&nbsp;Mention the code <span class="alert"><strong>World Congress on Computational Mechanics (WCCM)</strong></span> to receive our special room rate.</p>
									<p>The Congress special rate is valid until June 15, 2006.&nbsp;&nbsp;However, the block of rooms we reserved is nearly 70% filled as of March 22, 2006.&nbsp;&nbsp;When no more rooms remain in the block, or the June 15 cut-off date arrives, the regular room rate of $300 to $350 per night may apply at the Century Plaza Hotel.</p>
								<p>For information about other hotel amenities and features, and for directions to the hotel, please visit the hotel website.&nbsp;&nbsp;Alternatively, you may wish to consult Google&#8482; Maps at <a href="http://www.google.com/maps" target="_blank">http://www.google.com/maps</a> or MapQuest&reg; at <a href="http://www.mapquest.com" target="_blank">http://www.mapquest.com</a>.</p></td>
